{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189710/extras/logobarpg_1-4x.png?t=1733774909\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">An upcoming role-playing game centered around simulating the life of a bartender breathing life back into a run-down local city bar. Working night shifts, you will be tasked with pouring various cocktails for customers during fast-paced shifts, picked from a menu of your choosing. After each night, you will receive a payout depending on the quality of the drinks you poured. Using this money, you can customize the look and feel of the bar interior, your own apartment, as well as your player character. With thousands of player customization options and a branching narrative, you will be able to feel a sense of immersion as you maneuver your way through the story as it unfolds. Uncover the secrets of your manager, the shady landlord, as well as the mysterious &quot;last guy&quot;. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>BE YOUR OWN BARTENDER</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189710/extras/BARPG_PreRelease_Launch_Trailer_Prototype_-_Copy__1_.gif?t=1733774909\" />With thousands of possible character customization options, you can truly feel a part of the world you play in.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>BUILD YOUR OWN BAR</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189710/extras/BARPG_gif_ownbar.gif?t=1733774909\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Decorate the walls, play your style of music, curate your own menu. The bar 